arcade.sim.profiler

Class GraphProfiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.sim.profiler.Profiler
      • arcade.sim.profiler.GraphProfiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class GraphProfiler
extends Profiler
    Extension of Profiler to output graph structure and hemodynamic properties.

    The output JSON includes:

    • seed: random seed of the simulation
    • config: summary of model setup from toJSON method in Series
    • helpers: list of Helper objects
    • components: list of Component objects
    • timepoints: list of timepoints, where each timepoint contains lists of edges and nodes in the graph
    Since:
    2.3
    Version:
    2.3.3
